                  <scopecontent>
                     <p>Autograph notes to the poem, revised, in <persname normal="Gray, Thomas, 1716-1771">Gray</persname>'s copy of
									<extref href="https://www.thomasgray.org/cgi-bin/view.cgi?collection=primary&amp;edition=1757&amp;text=bapo"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <title render="italic" linktype="simple">Odes by Mr. Gray</title>
                        </extref> (<date normal="1757" type="publication" era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1757</date>).
								The notes were first published in the poem's version in <extref href="https://www.thomasgray.org/cgi-bin/view.cgi?collection=primary&amp;edition=1768&amp;text=bapo"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <title render="italic" linktype="simple">Poems</title>
                        </extref> (<date normal="1768" type="publication" era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1768</date>).
							</p>
